OL,3,CNottingham man waits to hear from
OL,4,Cfriend in train crash
OL,6,FTwo East Midlands Railway services
OL,7,Fhave been involved in a collision.
OL,8,FThey were the 4.40pm from Corby to
OL,9,FLondon St Pancras and the 3.50pm
OL,10,FNottingham to London St Pancras.
OL,12,FSpeaking at Nottingham train station,
OL,13,FOliver told ITV Central that his
OL,14,Ffriend was on the train when he heard
OL,15,Fthe news.
OL,17,F"It's just a shock really because you
OL,18,Fdon't expect the trains to collide at
OL,19,Fsuch speeds
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
