PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782233278
OL,3,CNottingham man waits to hear from
OL,4,Cfriend in train crash
OL,6,FIt later added: "We understand that
OL,7,Fpeople are concerned about relatives
OL,8,For friends who may have been
OL,9,Ftravelling on the trains involved in
OL,10,Fthe incident near Bedford.
OL,12,F"We're asking people not to travel to
OL,13,Fthe scene and await further updates
OL,14,Ffrom emergency services."
OL,16,FThe fire and rescue service said:
OL,17,F"Crews are currently in attendance at
OL,18,Fan incident on the railway just south
OL,19,Fof Bedford.
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@AOUvD@YO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
