PN,34805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782233278
OL,3,CNottingham man waits to hear from
OL,4,Cfriend in train crash
OL,6,F"Please avoid the area. Thank you for
OL,7,Fyour co-operation."
OL,9,FEast of England Ambulance Service
OL,10,Fsaid: "We have sent a number of
OL,11,Fresources, including air ambulance and
OL,12,Four Hazardous Area Response Team, to a
OL,13,Fmajor incident on the railway south of
OL,14,F_Bedford. We encourage people to avoid
OL,15,Fthe area.
OL,17,F"Further updates will be provided in
OL,18,Fdue course. Please only call 999 in an
OL,19,Femergency."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@SO]rD@GOUyD@AOU{D@KO]
